. Web App URLs Structure
5.1 Customer Web App (customerapp.localconnect.pune)
text
/                          # Homepage with service categories
/login                     # Customer login/signup
/services/:category        # Service category listing
/providers/:serviceId      # Provider selection for service
/book/:providerId         # Booking flow
/booking/:bookingId       # Booking details and tracking
/profile                  # Customer profile and addresses
/bookings                 # Booking history
/support                  # Customer support

----------------------------------------------------------
5.2 Service Provider Web App (provider.localconnect.pune)
text
/                         # Provider dashboard
/login                    # Provider login/signup
/profile                  # Business profile setup
/services                 # Service management
/bookings                 # Booking requests and management
/calendar                 # Availability calendar
/earnings                 # Financial dashboard
/customers               # Customer management

---------------------------------------------------------------------
5.3 Admin Panel (admin.localconnect.pune)
text
/                        # Admin dashboard with key metrics
/users                   # Customer management
/providers               # Provider verification and management
/bookings               # All bookings overview
/services               # Service category and pricing management
/analytics              # Business analytics and reports
/support                # Customer support tickets
----------------------------------------------------------------------
